[b]TVO - Allan Gregg in Conversation, September 26 2008: Mel Hurtig on 'The Truth about Canada'[/b]

The publisher, political activist and author argues we are no longer the people we think we are. He has combed world statistics to see how Canada really measures up and has published his important, astonishing, and truly appalling findings in [url=http://www.randomhouse.com/book/84639/the-truth-about-canada-by-mel-hurtig][i]The Truth about Canada[/i][/url]. 

